$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_attackables

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_attackables -  This method recalculates the hunting structure, and returns an array of people we are in the same room with, and who we can attack.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
object * query_attackables()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
returns an array of people on our attacker list that are in
the room with us

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/combat.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method recalculates the hunting structure, and returns an array
of people we are in the same room with, and who we can attack.
If we are on a horse in a room with someone, we start attacking them
as well.
.EP

